data.description: **Fishermen's Haven** This is an income producing property with Airbnb that stays booked! This home is 2 min from the locks to get in on the biggest lake in FL for some of the best bass fishing you could ask for. This 3-bedroom 2 bath with office space and Florida Room that can be used as a 4th bedroom, is in a quiet neighborhood and sits between 2 canals, you can park your boat in the front or pull it up to your dock in the back, next to your back patio. There is plenty of space for storage as there is a shed on the property. This property also has fruit trees that produce every year. The property also has a brand-new septic tank that was put in last year. The home has been converted to be handicap accessible. Call today to for a showing!
